product.product_title: Skechers Women's D'Lites Fresh Start Memory Foam Sneakers
product.cushioning: Signature Memory Foam insole provides plush, personalized cushioning for all-day wear.
product.breathability: Synthetic leather and mesh upper offers moderate breathability; the chunky design prioritizes structure.
product.short_description: Embrace the iconic chunky sneaker trend with the Skechers Women's D'Lites Fresh Start Memory Foam Sneakers. These shoes are a modern take on a '90s classic, offering a bold, fashion-forward silhouette without compromising on all-day comfort. The D'Lites Fresh Start features a durable synthetic leather and mesh upper in a clean, crisp white colorway, accented with subtle Skechers detailing for a timeless, versatile look that pairs effortlessly with everything from jeans and leggings to dresses. The substantial, multi-layered midsole is the defining feature, providing a sturdy, supportive base with a stylish, retro vibe. Inside, the shoe is equipped with Skechers' signature Memory Foam cushioned insole, which molds to your foot's unique shape for personalized, plush comfort and support with every step. A flexible traction outsole ensures stability. Make a fresh start with the Skechers D'Lites, the ultimate chunky sneaker for the woman who wants to make a statement while enjoying premium comfort.
product.about_this_item: REVITALIZED CLASSIC STYLE with smooth leather and synthetic upper; CUSHIONED COMFORT using Air-Cooled Memory Foam insole; LIGHTWEIGHT shock-absorbing midsole; FLEXIBLE rubber traction outsole for durability and grip.
